PROJECT NAME: Mineplace
PROJECT VERSION: Sub 1.0
PROJECT DESCRIPTION: Minecraft ripoff made for an Arduino Uno/Pro Mini with a 1.8" tft
                     display and a joystick (will be d-pad) control scheme.
